# Moderations API

## Endpoint
POST {{.BaseURL}}/v1/moderations

## Description
Classifies if text violates OpenAI's Usage Policies.

## Authentication
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY

## Example Request
```bash
curl {{.BaseURL}}/v1/moderations \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -d '{
    "input": "I want to kill them."
  }'
```

## Parameters
- **input** (required): Text to classify
- **model**: Moderation model (text-moderation-stable, text-moderation-latest)